com.scheid.jsondiff.service.compare

Interface JsonDiffCompare

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultJSONCompare, JSONContentCompare, JSONSizeCompare

    public interface JsonDiffCompare
    Interface to allow multiple implementations for JSON base64 encoded binary data comparison.

      • compare

        ComparisonResult compare(java.util.Set<ElementPair> elementPairs)
        Compare a Set of ElementPair to determine the possible differences.
        Parameters:
        elementPairs - Sets of ElementPair to be compared
        Returns:
        ComparisonResult The comparison result for each ElementPair provided. A comparison error, if present, will be displayed on comparisonError.
